@startuml ThesisManagementAPI-ActivityDiagram

title Thesis Management API - Thesis Submission Activity Diagram

|Student|
start
:Login to the system;
:Search for available topics;
:Select a topic;
:Submit thesis application;

|Tutor|
:Receive notification of new application;
:Review application;
if (Application approved?) then (yes)
    :Assign student to topic;
    |Student|
    :Receive notification of approval;
    :Work on the thesis;
    :Submit final thesis document;
    |Tutor|
    :Receive submitted thesis;
    :Review and grade the thesis;
    :Update thesis status to "Graded";
else (no)
    |Student|
    :Receive notification of rejection;
endif

stop

@enduml
